title: ONYPHE
description:
The ONYPHE enrichment connector is designed to leverage the Ctiscan category of data to enrich observables, providing detailed Internet scan data
 and mapping for open ports, protocols, banners and relationships â€” including ASNs, organizations, certificates,
 DNS domains, technologies, ports, countries and analytical pivots such as Ja4s.
 In addition the Indicators can be enriched using the 'onyphe' pattern to run threat-hunting queries within the OpenCTI platform and import matching observables.
short_description: ONYPHE connector enriches observables and indicators with Internet intelligence and mapping data.
